User Dashboard





Vendor Dashboard-->
1. Vendor Profile (Basic and Business Info, Documents)
2. Service List Management
3. Add New Service (with images, pricing, details)
4. Manage Bookings (View, Accept, Decline)
5. Booking Calendar / Schedule
6. Earnings / Payment Tracking
7. Reviews & Ratings Management
8. Settings (Notifications, Availability)



User Dashboard-->
1. Profile Management (Edit profile info, change password)
2. Booking History (View past, current, cancelled bookings)
3. Payment History
4. Notifications (System & Booking Updates)
5. Favorites / Wishlist
6. Settings (Notification preferences)








1. Call ke baad user ko kya dikhana chahiye?

Abhi tum sirf “Call” redirect de rahe ho. Problem ye hai ki:

App ko nahi pata call connect hui ya nahi
Booking hui ya nahi
Vendor ne response diya ya nahi

👉 Iska solution:

Call ke turant baad ek “Post-Call Flow” dikhao:

“Kya aapka kaam ho gaya?”
✅ Booked
❌ No Response
⏳ Still talking / Not decided
Isse kya fayda?
Tumhe conversion data milega (kitne calls → bookings)
Vendor ranking improve kar sakte ho (jo reliable hai wo upar)
Fake vendors filter kar sakte ho

👉 Advanced idea:

“Book Now” button bhi add karo (call ke bina direct booking request)
2. WhatsApp jaisa chat app ke andar banana – sahi ya galat?

Short answer:
👉 Early stage ke liye ❌ galat
👉 Scale hone ke baad ✔️ sahi

Kyun?
❌ Problem:
User already WhatsApp use karta hai
Usko naya chat system sikhana padega → friction
Development heavy hai
Realtime chat (socket, database, notifications)
Media sharing, read receipts, etc.
Trust issue
Log WhatsApp pe zyada comfortable hote hain
✔️ Better approach (abhi ke liye):

👉 WhatsApp redirect hi rakho + pre-filled message:

Example:

"Hi, mujhe AC repair chahiye, aap available ho kya?"

👉 Isse:

User ko easy lagta hai
Vendor ko clear requirement milti hai
Tumhara dev time bachta hai
🚀 Future (jab users badh jaye):

Tab tum:

In-app chat introduce kar sakte ho
Ya hybrid approach:
Chat start app me → continue WhatsApp pe
3. Tumhare app ke liye best flow (practical UX)
Step-by-step ideal flow:
User vendor list dekhe
Click vendor
Options:
📞 Call
💬 WhatsApp
📅 Request Booking
Jab “Call” kare:

➡️ Wapas aane par:

“Did you hire this vendor?”
“Rate your experience”
Jab “Booking Request” kare:

➡️ Vendor ko notification
➡️ User ko status:

Pending
Accepted
Rejected
4. Sabse important cheez jo tum miss kar rahe ho

👉 Trust layer

Add karo:

Ratings ⭐
Reviews
“Verified Vendor” badge
Response time

Yahi tumhare app ko local market me strong banayega.

5. Final clear verdict
✅ Post-call feedback system → must have
❌ Abhi WhatsApp jaisa chat banana → avoid karo
✅ WhatsApp redirect + pre-filled message → best for now
✅ Booking + rating system → high priority


















1. Reality check (important)
WhatsApp aur normal calls black box hote hain
Tum na messages read kar sakte ho
Na payment verify kar sakte ho
Na booking confirm automatically milti hai

👉 Isliye jo successful apps hain wo “estimate + user input” pe kaam karte hain, na ki spying pe.

2. Practical solution (jo actually kaam karta hai)
🔹 A. Post-action feedback (most important)

Call ya WhatsApp ke baad user ko push karo:

Popup / screen:

“Kya aapne is vendor ko hire kiya?”

Options:

✅ Haan, kaam ho gaya
❌ Nahi hua
⏳ Abhi baat chal rahi hai

👉 Ye tumhara primary signal hoga

🔹 B. Vendor side confirmation

Vendor panel me:

“Kya aapko is user se kaam mila?”

👉 Match karo:

User ne “yes” bola
Vendor ne “yes” bola

➡️ High confidence booking ✔️

🔹 C. Booking request system (strong tracking)

Tum ek aur layer add karo:

👉 “Request Booking” button

Flow:

User request bheje
Vendor accept kare
Status track ho:
Pending
Accepted
Completed

👉 Is case me tumhe clear data milega

🔹 D. Smart estimation (advanced)

Agar:

User ne call kiya
2–3 min baad app pe wapas aaya
Same vendor ko dobara open nahi kiya

👉 High chance = deal ho gayi

(ye perfect nahi hai, but useful signal hai)

3. Payment tracking ka kya?

👉 Agar tum external (cash/UPI directly vendor ko) allow karte ho:

❌ Tum track nahi kar sakte

👉 Agar tum app ke andar payment lana chahte ho:

✔️ Tab hi tumhe exact pata chalega

Lekin warning:

Payment system banana = high complexity + trust issue
Local market me log direct pay karna prefer karte hain

👉 Better:

Start without payment
Baad me introduce karo (optional)
4. Best hybrid model (recommended)

Tum ye combo use karo:

Call / WhatsApp
Booking Request button
Post-call feedback
Vendor confirmation
Ratings & reviews

👉 In sab ko combine karke:
tum 70–90% accuracy se samajh jaoge ki kaam hua ya nahi

5. Important mindset shift

Tumhara goal ye nahi hona chahiye:

“Mujhe exact pata chale kya baat hui”

Tumhara goal hona chahiye:

“Mujhe reliable signal mile ki kaam hua ya nahi”








